home.biography: I am a software developer with a primary focus on distributed systems, programming paradigms, and parallel computing. In this space, I delve into topics that bridge the gap between practical application and theoretical understanding, merging theory and practice in the realm of software development, while also sharing experiences and insights on computing.

metadata.description: This blog is about my journey as a Software Developer. Here do you find my thoughts, ideas, and experiences. I hope you enjoy it.
